'''Book of Revelation'''


==== Prokasovnni ====

Hem zhuz khunnanchea rupan dilam. Hea sogllea khunanchi somzonni diunk sompem nhoi; punn sadharonn khunna asat teo somzunk sompem :  “Jerusalem” mhollear Kristachi Povitr-Sobha; “Babilonia” vaittachi khunna ani tacho orth mhollear “sonvsarachi xokti”. Sorginchea Jerusaleak” Devache xokticho adar asa: sonvsari “ Babiloniek” khottea podviancho adar asa, toxench tea vorixtt aracho ani khottea provadiacho. Hea vhoddlea zhuzant chitram asat tim boreacheo ani vaittacheo khunna. Ankdde, xik’ke ani tuturi hem zhuz, cholta ani xevottak pavta mhonn dakhounk vaporleant.

Sat bandavollimnim Juanvan him chitram manddleant. Punn, eke-eke bandavollichi xim’khoi sompta tem dakhounk vivronnkaranchem ek mot na.

Patmos zunvear, sumar 96 vorsa, Juanvan, xubhvortomanachea boroinnaran, hem apnnak kel’le Prokasovnnechem Pustok boroilem.


